| File | Description |
|---|---|
| `{{ isa_name }}.decode` | Decodetree instruction decoder |
| `{{ isa_name }}_helpers.c` | Instruction behavior (one C helper per instruction) |
| `{{ isa_name }}_helper.h` | Helper declarations |
